Emergency services are at the scene of the crash in Jozini, KZN. KWAZULU-NATAL - A major accident has taken place in Jozini, KwaZulu-Natal. A truck ploughed into cars and pedestrians after the driver reportedly lost control of the vehicle. READ: Six injured in Durban crash Eight people have died and 32 were injured. The KwaZulu-Natal Emergency Rescue Service says 10 vehicles were involved.